fern
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:as a quasi-adj., or in loose combination or collocated with names of land features 'covered with fern, ferned'; esp. fern-flat, fern hill, fern ridge. cf. fern country, fernland. [nb AND fern-gully 1889]
